{"word":"G3986 - πειρασμός - peirasmós - pi-ras-mos' - Temptation","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πειρασμός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>peirasmós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pi-ras-mos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Temptation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சோதனை, சோதித்தல் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"an experiment, attempt, trial, proving, temptation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3985 - πειράζω - peirázō - pi-rad'-zo/3985\">G3985</a>; a putting to <i>proof</i> (by experiment [of good], <i>experience</i> [of evil], solicitation, discipline or provocation); by implication <i>adversity:</i> - temptation, X try."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1598 - ἐκπειράζω - ekpeirázō - ek-pi-rad'-zo/1598\">G1598</a>, <a href=\"#/G3984 - πεῖρα - peîra - pi'-rah/3984\">G3984</a>, <a href=\"#/G3985 - πειράζω - peirázō - pi-rad'-zo/3985\">G3985</a>, <a href=\"#/G3986 - πειρασμός - peirasmós - pi-ras-mos'/3986\">G3986</a>, <a href=\"#/G3987 - πειράω - peiráō - pi-rah'-o/3987\">G3987</a>, <a href=\"#/G551 - ἀπείραστος - apeírastos - ap-i'-ras-tos/551\">G551</a>"}]}